        "title": "docs(channels): add Pinclaw hardware voice channel",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds channel documentation for [Pinclaw](https://pinclaw.ai), a hardware voice interface plugin available on ClawHub.\n\nPinclaw is a BLE wearable device with an iOS companion app that connects to OpenClaw as a voice channel. The plugin is published on ClawHub as a community code plugin (`clawhub:pinclaw`) and on npm (`pinclaw`).\n\n### Changes\n\n- **`docs/channels/pinclaw.md`** — Full channel doc covering install, setup, configuration, device skills, server tools, and capabilities table. Follows the existing channel doc conventions.\n- **`docs/channels/index.md`** — Added Pinclaw entry in alphabetical order under Supported channels.\n\n### Plugin details\n\n- ClawHub listing: [clawhub.ai/plugins/ericshang98/pinclaw](https://clawhub.ai/plugins/ericshang98/pinclaw)\n- npm: [npmjs.com/package/pinclaw](https://www.npmjs.com/package/pinclaw)\n- Source: [github.com/ericshang98/pinclaw](https://github.com/ericshang98/pinclaw) (plugin directory)\n- Install: `openclaw plugins install clawhub:pinclaw`",
